## âš™ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Backend**: Python 3.13+, FastAPI, OpenAI Async SDK  
- **Vector DB**: Qdrant  
- **Frontend**: React 18, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, Framer Motion  
- **AI**: OpenAI Embeddings + Chat completions  
- **Containers**: Docker + Docker Compose

