## ğŸ“ Architecture

```
[React UI] <---> [FastAPI API] <---> [Qdrant DB]
                               |
                          [OpenAI API]
```

- Commits = vectors + metadata  
- Quests = templates + similarity search  
- Quest engine = embedding lookup â†’ LLM prompt â†’ custom quest

